data.description: RECENT PRICE IMPROVEMENT!   Welcome to this oversized, double wide manufactured home with 2 additions added. Best part is...NO HOA and lots of land! This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, living room, family room and even extra living space which can be for an office or flex area.  The kitchen and master bathroom have custom wood cabinetry, which offers lots of storage.  This home has so much potential and is perfect for a large family.  Enjoy sitting out on either the front porch or out back on the deck and enjoy the beautiful views. You'll love the detached 1 car garage and added storage room in the backyard. Lots of parking available on this property, even for an RV or a Boat!  A ride on lawnmower conveys so you can have some fun while mowing the grass.  HVAC replaced 2018, Roof 2010. All measurements and square footage are approximate and not guaranteed. Buyers are responsible for verification of all information. Square footage is approximate and probably more than listed since additions have been made.
